{"text": "This force directed forwards the centre is called the centripetal force.", "fibs": ["force"]}
{"text": "For a stone rotated in a circle by a string, the centripetal force is provided by the tension in the string.", "fibs": ["stone"]}
{"text": "The centripetal force for motion of a planet around the sun is the gravitational force on the planet due to the sun.", "fibs": ["force"]}
{"text": "For a car taking a circular turn on a horizontal road, the centripetal force is the force of friction.", "fibs": ["car"]}
